Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}命运也是推理的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.32,0:00:06.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}神秘的事件也能看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}夏季之末的高原旅社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.14,0:00:09.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}唯一小路上的不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.81,0:00:11.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在找寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.46,0:00:26.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经习惯了谎言 现在也是一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有能够确定的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使一个人也不能哭泣 软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.55,0:00:51.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.53,0:00:59.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Oh yeah. You're going nowhere. It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}切实地前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.77,0:01:28.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}感受现在 you're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.96,0:01:46.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}疗养森林的不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}（疗养森林旅馆由此去）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.18,0:01:52.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这里交通这么不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}你们还会想来玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.77,0:01:55.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k101}要到我们旅馆去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}就只有穿过这片森林 除此之外没有其他道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过 只要再开10分钟就到旅馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k286}请各位再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.76,0:02:06.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k133}请问 我们要去的这家旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.16,0:02:10.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}是你们兄弟俩在经营的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.18,0:02:13.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}不是的 其实我只有在夏天的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}才会到我哥哥的旅馆来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.90,0:02:20.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}对了 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.18,0:02:23.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}我们不是要把西瓜送去给爸爸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}可是 总得先把客人送到旅馆去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要去别的地方啊 那正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}不知道能不能借用一下厕所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.02,0:02:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k106}过了那座桥就是我爸爸的家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}爸爸你就是喝太多啤酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}是多了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}舒服多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个花瓶还真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}村长伯伯是陶艺家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.44,0:03:21.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k238}不 那只是我一个人打发时间随便做做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天手受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}现在恐怕还做不了陶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}这是我家田里长的西瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}请尝尝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k163}是想借钱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}爸爸 哥哥没有那么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}这里没你说话的份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}我当时那么反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.41,0:03:43.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}你却非要去入赘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}听着 紫郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k142}我不会借钱给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}拿着瓜赶紧走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}刚才让你们见笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}今天我好像说错了话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 我爸爸总是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}不光顽固 而且观念守旧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}下午好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.18,0:04:12.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}蓝子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k96}在收牛奶费吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k146}本来想去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}可是忘记带账本了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}我先把牛奶费交了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.55,0:04:21.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k241}谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k73}不过 下次再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}那样账目清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}初次见面 蓝子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}我是私家侦探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.20,0:04:35.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天准备在紫郎先生的旅社住一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}房间是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k139}对不起 我还要去送牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:40.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}疗养森林的美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.92,0:04:54.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.21,0:04:56.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}请小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}河里很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}我去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好了 拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.32,0:05:12.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}给你 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k162}还好没弄湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}可是紫郎先生的裤子弄湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过被你们发现我不会游泳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 我们去摘做晚饭用的野菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其他的事情都交给里面的钟点工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}下午好 你订购的啤酒送来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}总是麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天有旅行团住吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯…算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啤酒没了 啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:20.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}这么快就喝醉睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.85,0:06:27.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}紫郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.85,0:06:28.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}野菜已经摘好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.86,0:06:30.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}是…是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:35.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}突然想起点事来 就先回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}是啊 不过请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}弟弟会摘野菜回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 这里是毛利侦探事务所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么 村长被人杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:06.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k129}好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}马上就过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.94,0:07:11.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你就是毛利小五郎先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}我是绿川洋二巡查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:26.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}先看看现场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}好 请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.65,0:07:36.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}裁纸刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}这就是凶器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}R.M.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}是名字的缩写吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}这是村长最喜欢的裁纸刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}根据遗体的状况来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.91,0:07:50.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}犯人进入书房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.85,0:07:53.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}从正面刺杀了进来的村长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}文件撒了一地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}说明犯人可能在寻找什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}关于犯人进来的路径
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}除了大门以外 其他入口都从里面上了锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.90,0:08:08.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蓝子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k109}请详细说说发现村长遗体时的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k107}我记得是4点差5分的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}我来收牛奶费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}当时 他在这个账本上盖了印章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}去紫郎先生的旅社途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.12,0:08:30.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我听见了惨叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k171}就马上回到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}然后就看见村长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}听见惨叫是在什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}是4点整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}当时我正在巡查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}比蓝子小姐来得稍微晚一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.78,0:08:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我记得是4点5分左右到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.81,0:08:55.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k159}村长是在蓝子小姐离开这里之后几分钟里被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k98}蓝子小姐来收牛奶费的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}犯人就很有可能已经在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k78}钱和信用卡好像都没有被偷走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}只是桌子上的东西掉下来了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}好像不是盗窃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.46,0:09:17.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}混蛋 不是说了不让你乱碰的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看来 是犯人来拜访村长的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}与村长发生了争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k102}一时冲动而杀害了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}顺便问问 你们二人4点整的时候在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我已经回到旅社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.83,0:09:37.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}我大概是在回来的路上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有人能证明吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:46.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}紫郎先生在蓝子小姐打来电话的4点10分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经在旅社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k174}另外 金次先生在电话还没打完的时候回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.02,0:09:53.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我们怎么会把爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}从爸爸家到旅社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}步行的话要花1小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}开车的话要花5分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}当时我们是步行出门的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}汽车一直放在旅社里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}还有其他的交通手段吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:12.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}旅社是那条唯一的小路的终点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}路的两侧山势险要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.33,0:10:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k122}10分钟内不可能从村长家回到旅社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样的话是蓝子小姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}不 从伤口的情况看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}犯人身上应该溅满了鲜血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.33,0:10:42.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}也就是说 在场的诸位都不可能犯案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.26,0:10:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人是入室行窃之后又杀了人的外部犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}总有什么地方不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k178}是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}姐姐 能给我看看账本吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.06,0:11:00.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k95}可以啊 孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.31,0:11:20.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这些文件都是村长今天处理的 日期都是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.82,0:11:30.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 我们能不能先回旅社去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}咦 粘土少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.79,0:11:44.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}村长手受伤了 不可能会用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 原来上面放着的绳子不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你怎么了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.25,0:12:01.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k77}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}没什么 我知道犯人是谁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人就在你们之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.28,0:12:24.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}你刚才不是说在场的诸位都不可能犯案吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蓝子小姐最先被排除出嫌疑范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.36,0:12:35.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人必须要处理沾了血的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是她却没有换衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}并且她也没有时间擦掉血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}紫郎先生和金次先生换了衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我和金次摘野菜的时候弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以换了衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.14,0:12:53.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}但是 如果犯人在这两人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他是怎么在10分钟之内回到旅社的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.81,0:12:59.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他是顺着河漂流下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}顺着村长家和旅社附近流过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}那条叫纲川的河漂流下来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.41,0:13:11.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}两三分钟就能回到旅社了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 河岸上没有能停船的栈桥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.87,0:13:20.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 而且这是一时冲动而发生的杀人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人并没有事先准备船只
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.33,0:13:27.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是说犯人是顺着河游下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么我不会游泳 就不是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}难道是金次先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}不要胡说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}请先听我说完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人可能是一时冲动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k298}杀害了村长后准备逃跑时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.97,0:13:49.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}发现自己浑身是血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}于是就想尽快离开村长家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.54,0:13:56.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}把自己身上的血迹洗干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这时他想到一个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}利用墙角里放的粘土和绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}粘土和绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}到底是怎么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:12.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}犯人先把沾了血的裤子脱下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.09,0:14:16.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在房间的水池里稍微冲洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}抱起粘土和绳子就离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后 把弄湿的裤子从里往外翻过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在内侧涂上粘土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.72,0:14:27.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}接着再把裤子翻回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}用绳子系住两个裤腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后 拿着裤腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}一边往裤子里充气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}一边从桥上跳到河里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.20,0:14:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}裤子里面充了气 形成一个充气筏子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人就靠着这个漂流到了下游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.52,0:14:54.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}孩子们常常在浴室用湿毛巾罩住空气玩耍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.25,0:14:56.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}和这个的原理是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.87,0:15:02.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}在裤子内侧涂上粘土可以防止漏气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}剩下的就靠河水的流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确一下子就能到达旅社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}血迹也基本冲洗干净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之后 犯人匆忙换了衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}平静地出现在我们面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那到底谁是犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在这之前 蓝子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k118}这个账本恐怕要作为证据上交
